Trust us, you don’t want to miss them. :)

2.Click on the weather card to check the 7 days weather forecast.

1. Customize your avatar now, use photo of your choice.
2.  "Connect to PC" optimized
3. Improvement in Russian, Spanish and Arabic languages
4. Bugs fixed and other improvements

Our message center is online now. Stay tuned. 
Several bugs have been fixed. More stable to transfer.
If you have any suggestion, please email us: feedback_ios@ushareit.com.

－Kindly added Sleep Timer which allows you to customize auto-off time.
－Support music searching.

If you think our app is great, please give us a five-star rating. If you have any advice or suggestions, feel free to let us know: feedback_ios@ushareit.com

We specially improved the performances related to file transfer. 

1.Supported transferring extra-large files exceeding 20G. 

2.Improved stability: transferring hundreds of thousands of files and contacts nonstop for 24 hours with no mistake.

3.Audio files recorded in SHAREit Pro and SHAREit Vault can be sent through SHAREit. 

4.Perfectly adaptable to iOS10.
